{
  "texts": [
    "5 More detailed description of the datasets can be found in He et al.",
    "4 The evaluation datasets included four health-related social media datasets: Health Care Reform (\"HCR\"), Human Papillomavirus (\"HPV\") Vaccine, COVID-19 Masking (\"Mask\"), and Vitals.com Physician Reviews (\"Vitals\").",
    "A non-health dataset, the IMDB Dataset (\"IMDB\") created from movie reviews, was used for baseline comparison.",
    "To reduce the cost of OpenAI API usage, we randomly sampled 1,000 posts from the Vitals dataset and the IMDB dataset, respectively.",
    "The HCR dataset was originally created by Speriosu et al."
  ]
}